# ElysianVista Project Overview

ElysianVista is a SaaS platform for real estate agencies to create branded websites and manage their listings. The platform supports multi-tenancy with different user roles and permissions.

## User Roles

| Role          | Usage Scope                                     |
| ------------- | ----------------------------------------------- |
| Admin         | Configure agency, manage listings & users       |
| Manager       | Assign properties, handle leads, oversee agents |
| Agent         | Manage assigned listings, interact with leads   |
| Secretary     | Support role for agent tasks                    |
| Buyer/Visitor | Search listings, contact agents via public site |

## Core Features

- Multi-tenant architecture with subdomain routing
- Role-based access control
- Property listing management
- White-labeled agency websites with customization
- Lead management system
- Image and file storage with Supabase
- Stripe integration for billing

## Main Application Components

- Admin Dashboard: Agency management portal
- Public Site: Customer-facing property listings
- API: Serves both dashboard and public sites

